Text:
Este disco no me gusta mucho, lo mio es la musica electronica, pero no he podido evitar la tentacion de subir un torrent que rapidamente va a tener un monton de semillas.
No hace falta que lo compartas, el torrent se mantiene solo.

This disc does not love me, mine is electronic music, but I could not avoid the temptation to quickly upload a torrent that will have a lot of seeds.
No need to share it, the torrent is kept alone.
Picked me up, took me out, raped me, and never called me again.  The perfect woman!
